docs.abstract: Tenants of three Upper West Side apartment buildings built by Donald Trump are petitioning to remove Trump name from their places of residence, citing embarrassment associated with name during presidential election; Equity Residential, company that manages buildings, says it has contractual obligation to maintain name.

headline.main: What’s in a Name? When It’s ‘Trump Place,’ It’s a Revolt
